'''Wolfgang Freyberg''' (born April 12, 1956) is a [[Germany|German]] [[historian]] and [[slavicist]]. Freyberg was born in [[Göttingen]], [[Lower Saxony]] and studied at the [[University of Göttingen]]. Since 1985 he is the director of the [[Cultural Center East Prussia]] in [[Ellingen]], [[Bavaria]].<ref name="bel">{{cite web |url=http://www.kulturzentrum-ostpreussen.de/mitarbeiter.php |title=  Apl. Professor|website=kulturzentrum-ostpreussen.de|publisher=[[Cultural Center East Prussia]] |access-date=18 August 2017 |quote=}}</ref>

